### ========================================
### LIKES TESTS
### ========================================
@host = {{$dotenv HOST}}
@access_token = {{$dotenv ACCESS_TOKEN}}

### 1. Like Post
POST {{host}}/posts/1/like
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 2. Unlike Post
POST {{host}}/posts/1/unlike
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 3. Get Like Status
GET {{host}}/posts/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### 4. Get Liked Users (Public)
GET {{host}}/posts/1/likes
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}